<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>好久不见 on 凉都小道</title><link>https://ronggle.com/tags/%E5%A5%BD%E4%B9%85%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%81/</link><description>Recent content in 好久不见 on 凉都小道</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>Soi</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 24 Oct 2015 21:26:33 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ronggle.com/tags/%E5%A5%BD%E4%B9%85%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%81/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>好久不见</title><link>https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/</link><pubDate>Sat, 24 Oct 2015 21:26:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/1.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 好久不见" />&lt;p>“我来到 你的城市 走过你来时的路 想像着 没我的日子 你是怎样的孤独”&amp;mdash;陈奕迅《好久不见》&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/1.jpg"
width="723"
height="564"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/1_hudca41cb8c7bbd2d1490a6c94ff30931c_52404_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/1_hudca41cb8c7bbd2d1490a6c94ff30931c_52404_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="1.jpg"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="307px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>每次看着这张图，我都会莫名的悲伤。看着这孤独的背影，倍感凄凉。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>初识，在那涂炭的血池，魔君肆虐，你我携手共进。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不知为何，我竟如此这般迷恋于你，你的可爱与天真，烂漫了我的世界，甚至使其崩塌。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我向你表达了我的爱慕，你没有拒绝，三生石旁，我许你三生七世，若有负于你，愿永堕阎罗。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我不曾为你准备什么，只是结发，成为夫妻，没有婚礼，没人宾客，你我相拥凝望。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/2.jpg"
width="800"
height="424"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/2_hu99554a95557b136b490ff457db8c54e7_786496_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/2_hu99554a95557b136b490ff457db8c54e7_786496_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="2"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="188"
data-flex-basis="452px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>从此江湖，你我相伴，我们去过星界，去过中州，去过西陆，去过雪国，去过沧海、大荒、荧惑岛，在北部雪国是一片冰雪荒芜之地，我们看着雪白的世界，忘却了流离的生活。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/3.jpg"
width="800"
height="409"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/3_hu93f0b6f826b07b1b692811e400e6486c_463183_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/3_hu93f0b6f826b07b1b692811e400e6486c_463183_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="3"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="195"
data-flex-basis="469px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>仙魔大战，你为了守护我，甘愿与我同为魔族，从此走上黑暗，而我，在不停的战斗中辗转，你只是静静的守候着我，什么都不说，偶尔停下来，我凝望着你的双眸，泛着忧伤。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/4.jpg"
width="690"
height="520"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/4_hueb7d94073ac0707080a150de78d9c81b_44154_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/4_hueb7d94073ac0707080a150de78d9c81b_44154_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="4"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="132"
data-flex-basis="318px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>而如今，我强大到可以独挡一面，你却不知去向。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/5.jpg"
width="705"
height="571"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/5_hu35d99dfa622c8075fe277c3b3267de0e_89780_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/5_hu35d99dfa622c8075fe277c3b3267de0e_89780_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="5"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="123"
data-flex-basis="296px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>没有你，我戎马半生，得到天下又能怎么样？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/6.jpg"
width="657"
height="511"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/6_hu224b985ce200f6a07f0622b14713da4b_64497_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/6_hu224b985ce200f6a07f0622b14713da4b_64497_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="6"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="308px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我独自一人，去过我们去过的每一个地方，看我们看过的每一处美景，却只能感受到孤独和忧伤。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>或许，我们此生，都不会再见，而我，注定孤独&amp;hellip;..&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/7.jpg"
width="762"
height="508"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/7_hu8da7f7da59a9b43be4f5248df5b93577_60494_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/7_hu8da7f7da59a9b43be4f5248df5b93577_60494_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="7"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="150"
data-flex-basis="360px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>每一天活在思念的池子里，游不出来，又或者不愿意出来&amp;hellip;..&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/8.jpg"
width="673"
height="564"
srcset="https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/8_hu047ea60e07bf3dcd5a0af9db57daaebe_58776_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ronggle.com/2015/it-is-been-a-long-time/8_hu047ea60e07bf3dcd5a0af9db57daaebe_58776_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="100% 100%"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="119"
data-flex-basis="286px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如果天黑之前来得及，我要忘了你眼睛，静静等候，余下的七世三生!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>